title: Are Any of Your Memories Real?
itunes:title: Are Any of Your Memories Real?
description:
There is a chance the very few memories that you have actually happened exactly the way you remember them happening. That being said, can we trust anyone's memories? Well in this episode, I am going to teach you the 3 things that happen to someone's brain when they recall memories and tell you stories.

Follow me on IG here: https://instagram.com/robdialjr
